<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>CWGame Asia - OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .otp-code-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .warning ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Verification Code</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= fullName %>,</p>

            <p>Use the following one-time password (OTP) to complete your verification process for CWGame Asia:</p>

            <div class="otp-code-container">
                <div class="otp-code">
                    <%= otpCode %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>This code is valid for <strong><%= expiryTime %></strong>. Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>Security Reminder:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>CWGame Asia will never ask for this code.</li>
                    <li>Never share your OTP with anyone, including our support team.</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>If you need help, contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@cwgameasia.com">support@cwgameasia.com</a>.</p>

            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>CWGame Asia Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</p>
            <p>Need help? <a href="https://cwgameasia.com/support">Visit our Support Center</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
